            "html_content": "<h2>It’s not about direct force. It’s about <span style=\"color: #CFD821;\">rotational torque.</span>\n</h2>\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, most brain injury is caused by rotational torque, not direct force. The hidden damage occurs when the skull spins around the brain. Nuro is the first solution designed from the ground up to address rotational torque comprehensively and intelligently.</p>"
